net.dempsy.lifecycle.annotation

Class MessageProcessor<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dempsy.lifecycle.annotation.MessageProcessor<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageProcessorLifecycle<T>

    public class MessageProcessor<T>
extends Object
implements MessageProcessorLifecycle<T>
    This class holds the MP prototype, and supports invocation of MP methods on an instance.
